    {
      "id": 2807,
      "category": "researcher",
      "content": "When applying for monthly billing (a line of credit), it was possible to intercept the request made to get your Uber account statistics (i.e. how many trips you've taken, total spend, etc...) and change this, which could possibly affect (in your favor) the outcome of a credit check. Overall, this was well handled by the taxi drivers and I am happy to keep my personal rating for Uber bug bounty...........10 out of 10.",
